node.text:
Drake's 'Certified Lover Boy' has now sold over 500,000 units in the US, making it the first album to reach this milestone in under a week in 2021, in this shot he was wearing a @jacobandco Astronomia ‘Casino’ Tourbillon in 18k rose gold. This masterpiece is the first grand complication timepiece with a roulette wheel that spins, allowing the owners to play their favorite game of chance at any time. At the press of the button at 8 o’clock position of the case, the roulette wheel is forcefully spun, sending the little white ceramic ball flying. One of the 18 pieces produced is owned by @thenotoriousmma . #JacobandCo

Limited edition: 18 pieces
Retail price: $ 620,000.00

Photo: @gettyimages | @jacobandco

node.text:
The Italian motorcycle racer @andreaiannone wears a limited @geraldcharles_official Maestro GC3.0 in rose gold with green ‘emerald’ dial, part of brand’s Premier 2021. This timepiece is powered by an hand finished ultra-thin automatic chronograph movement called GCA3022/12 made by Vaucher. The case back of the watch shows the limited edition number engraved and the words ‘Premier 2021’ lasered on the sapphire crystal. #GeraldCharles

Limited edition: 25 pieces
Retail price: $ 43,000.00

Photo: @_marc_lucas | @geraldcharles_official

node.text:
@platinumtimesco has now available an exclusive @richardmille RM055 Automatic ‘Asia Edition’ made in partnership with the golfer Bubba Watson. This 30-piece limited edition is made in ceramic and was available only for the Asian market. It features a skeletonized movement with a caramel inner bezel and rose gold colored hands with luminous hour markers. #RichardMille

Photo: @platinumtimesco

node.text:
@antogriezmann is officially back to Atletico Madrid, during today’s presentation was wearing a @patekphilippe Nautilus Chronograph 5980/1R in 18k rose gold. This timepiece presents a black gradient dial with rose gold applied hour markers and luminescent coating. This reference over the years became one of the most appreciated of Patek Philippe, worn by some of the most influential celebrities. #PatekPhilippe

Retail price: $97,500.00
Market price: $250,000.00

Photo: @atleticodemadrid | @patekphilippe

node.text:
The UEFA Champions League winner @kaihavertz29 of Chelsea FC and Germany National Team ahead of 2022 FIFA World Cup Qualifier match was wearing a green @patekphilippe Aquanaut 5168G in 18k white gold. This model is not the first Aquanaut in khaki green. In 2011, Patek released a highly limited “special clients only” green Aquanaut Jumbo 5167A in a 40mm stainless steel case. At 42.2mm, its case is larger than that of the 5167. The ref. 5168G was added to the collection in 2019. #PatekPhilippe 

Retail price: $40,615.00
Market price: $95,000.00

Photo: @dfb_team | @patekphilippe

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Monte-Carlo, Monaco with @patekphilippe, and @_1_5_1_8_. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
An exclusive-look to the unique @patekphilippe Nautilus 5719/11G-010 in 18k white gold set with diamonds and blue sapphires. Introduced in 2015 together with the emeralds and rubies versions, these masterpieces were exclusively available to three special clients of the brand. The dial is set with 255 brilliant-cut diamonds and 3 baguette-cut blue sapphires as hour markers. The insane bezel features 32 baguette-cut blue sapphires while the center links of the bracelet are set with 150 baguette-cut diamonds. How much do you think this watch could fetch on auction considering that is a unique piece? #PatekPhilippe

Photo: @_1_5_1_8_

Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Monte-Carlo, Monaco with @maxverstappen1, and @rolex. May be an image of 3 people and wrist watch.

node.text:
The F1 racing driver @maxverstappen1 of Red Bull Racing team wins the 2021 Dutch Grand Prix to reach the first position of the driver standings overtaking Lewis Hamilton. In this recent shot the Dutch driver was wearing a @rolex Cosmograph Daytona in 18k yellow gold with champagne dial and black chronograph sub-dials. Introduced in 2017 this timepiece presents a black cerachrom bezel with an oysterflex bracelet, making it the first Daytona to be fitted on a rubber strap. This reference is getting hard to get from Rolex authorized dealers, following the hype of stainless steel version. #Rolex

Retail price: $ 32,550.00
Market price: $ 45,000.00

Photo: @riccardopatreseofficial | @rolex

node.text:
The Russian model @ksenia_tsaritsina wears a @jacobandco Brilliant Deco Tourbillon in 18k white gold set with 287 baguette-diamonds and one rose-cut diamond. The openworked dial presents brilliant-cut set bridges with 178 diamonds. Jacob & Co. has access to the very best sources of diamonds and gemstones from all over the world. Many of the gem-set timepieces, like the Brilliant Art Deco Skeleton Tourbillon pieces, require meticulous care in the choosing of stones for quality, cut, clarity, and matching color. #JacobandCo

Limited edition: 18 pieces
Retail price: $ 770,000.00

Photo: @ksenia_tsaritsina | @jacobandco

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by INSANE LUXURY in Los Angeles, California with @champagnepapi, and @richardmille. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text:
@champagnepapi paid $2.2 million dollars for his new @richardmille RM 27-04 ‘Rafael Nadal’ Tourbillon as mentioned in ‘You Only Live Twice’ lyrics: “Yeah, two-point-two for the Rafael Nadal”. Limited to just 50 pieces (sold out), as the other four Nadal Tourbillon produced, this watch features a calibre based on a microblasted string mesh that is brand new to watchmaking. Formed from a single woven steel cable measuring just 0.27 mm in diameter and held in place by two turnbuckles. Drake's has broken the 2021 record for most-streamed artist and album in a day on Apple Music and Spotify. #RichardMille

Limited edition: 50 pieces
Retail price: $ 1,027,000.00

Photo: Drake - Way 2 Sexy (YouTube) | @richardmille

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by INSANE LUXURY on September 05, 2021 tagging @skeletonconceptofficial. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
Introducing the @skeletonconceptofficial Maldonado Concept, a watch inspired by the world of racing cars and F1. The Maldonado Concept timepiece has a special design made in partnership with the Venezuelan racing driver @pastormaldo who competed in @f1 for the Williams (2011–2013) and Lotus (2014–2015) teams @pastormaldo. This spectacular watch pushes the limits and the codes of the Daytona 116520 furthermore, thanks to its skeletonized design and the blue-ish & grey palette tones used on the dial. The bezel is made in titanium (the highest level of quality for this material) gives it a smooth and minimalist aspect. #SkeletonConcept

Photo: @skeletonconceptofficial
